<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>MAKE US HOLY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Lalpa, hun hih thiengtho in,
 Ka lungthima um haw hi;
 Utna haw leh talent cheng cheng,
 Nang chawihat na'n Na siem hi.

[V2]
 Lampi thiengah,
 Gammang lo di'n ei pui in.

[V3]
 2. Nang ngeiin nei puihuoi thiem hi,
 Lam dika petmang lo di'n;
 Changlam ahim, veilam ahim,
 Thildang in ei hun hip sek.

[V4]
 Aw Lopi pen,
 Ei veng inla, ei puiin.

[V5]
 3. Na umzie a thil bul cheng cheng,
 Nangmah hun suhawih haw kha;
 Ka lungthim ale hun tuh in,
 Chun, hinna gah hawih intin.

[V6]
 Pakcha bangin,
 Ka tawihdan hun sulang in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>349</hymn_number>
</song>